  "link": "http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543157/", 
  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t这一周可谓风起云涌，各路新闻看得人眼花缭乱。细观之发现微博这一新平台的身影总是隐于其后，不管是最近焦点的济南中院，还是陆续被带走的大V们，都让这个信息膨胀的时代抖了一抖。</p>\n<p>\n\t有人说济南中院官微此举对于中国法治建设有举足轻重的作用，有人甚至称之为里程碑式的创举。但不管根源在哪儿，&ldquo;公开&rdquo;这二字，总算是有了他的光彩。</p>\n<p>\n\t微博这一平台的兴起在推动我们社会发展的同时，也制造出来了新的话题、名词跟事件。微博打拐，微博公益，随手拍还有红极一时的郭美美事件、凤姐事件、干露露现象、&ldquo;XXX滚出娱乐圈&rdquo;的话题等。</p>\n<p>\n\t而最近，作业本被封号，薛蛮子被刑拘，秦火火等人被刑拘。这一番大动作，让人见识到，看似平静的水面下是怎样的波涛汹涌。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t刨去官方的意图，众位网民们在某些人的肆意撺掇下，打着各种旗号卫道。这其中，是否不乏不理性的做法？是否有&ldquo;帮凶&rdquo;之嫌？</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tComparing with participating to the topic, I would like to read it and just treat it as a piece of news for the reason that why this topic would become the hotpots confused me a lot but I can not find a cause. Besides that, the messages which the others gave us always contain the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/crytic\" target=\"_blank\">crytic</a> information they wanted to give us. Take the Mr. Li's case as an example. When the thing exploded by the media, it always is carrying the words like someone's son or the rich's son which will give a bad impression to the public.</p>\n<p>\n\tAll in all, the words the massages used may contain personal impression but the public can not know that, as the result, the public may be the weapon of some bad guys to attack others or achieve some goals they want. So we need to get more information from more aspects when we have the willing to criticize someone or something.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong><br />\n\tSome persons, for instance Qin huohuo, who is reported to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/smear\" target=\"_blank\">smear</a> Red Cross, prefer to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/disperse\" target=\"_blank\">disperse</a> fake information on the Internet. The information is always used by &ldquo;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/patriot\" target=\"_blank\">patriot</a>&rdquo; to make public hatred of the Party. It is common to see some news, which is out of time packed with something new and put on the famous social web like weibo and renren. Some household stars use their fame to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/intersperse\" target=\"_blank\">intersperse</a> these <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/dummy\" target=\"_blank\">dummy</a> message to raise their popularity. If the Internet environment is purified, the famous should shoulder responsibility to distinguish the false information. Meanwhile, the public security also should strengthen <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/punitive\" target=\"_blank\">punitive</a> measure to standardize the Internet rule and stop from the original.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/813536/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543157/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543157\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h